## 🚀 Başlangıç Adımları (Sıralı)

### Adım 1 — Ortam Kurulumu
```bash
# PostgreSQL kur (lokal veya Docker)
docker run --name eee-db -e POSTGRES_PASSWORD=secret -p 5432:5432 -d postgres

# Gemini API key al → https://aistudio.google.com/
```

### Adım 2 — Backend Kurulumu
```bash
mkdir eee-chat && cd eee-chat
mkdir backend && cd backend
npm init -y
npm install express prisma @prisma/client typescript ts-node
npm install @google/generative-ai multer jsonwebtoken bcrypt
npx prisma init
```

### Adım 3 — Frontend Kurulumu
```bash
cd ..
npx create-next-app@latest frontend --typescript --tailwind --app
cd frontend
npm install axios zustand @radix-ui/react-dialog lucide-react
npm install react-markdown remark-math rehype-katex katex
```

